OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FAny daytime
OL,6,Fshowers will gradually ease to leave a
OL,7,Fdry night, with prolonged clear
OL,8,Fspells. Winds easing, and turning
OL,9,Flocally chilly, with a patchy frost
OL,10,Fforming in prone rural spots.
OL,11,
OL,12,CMonday:FAfter a bright and chilly
OL,13,Fstart, the clouds will begin to bubble
OL,14,Fup to give sunny spells and showers,
OL,15,Flocally heavy with hail and thunder,
OL,16,Finto the afternoon. Light winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
