OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FDry
OL,6,Fwith sunny spells Tuesday, after
OL,7,Fanother chilly start. Breezier on
OL,8,FWednesday, cloud and outbreaks of rain
OL,9,Fmoving erratically east. Sunny spells
OL,10,Fand isolated showers Thursday.
OL,11,FTemperatures near normal.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
